review_blob: Loved this beer when it was around. Honestly this is based on what i remember from this. But i really did like it!

I like the style of this beer. Had bottle and can. Thai cans are terrible, stick to the bottle. Its not 5% in thailand its 6.4% but varies. Impossible to rate because it changes. Good cold. Good cheap beer.
Nice smelling. Amber. Semi complex caramel/coffee flavors. Wonderful aftertaste. NIce beer.
